note right of "arithmetic"
  src/operations/arithmetic.py
  Delegates to a module-level CalculationEngine
  instance (_engine) to avoid code duplication.
  Not used by the main dispatch chain (Calculator /
  OperationRegistry); available for direct import.
end note

note right of "roots"
  src/operations/roots.py
  Standalone implementations of factorial, square,
  cube, square_root, cube_root — mirror of the
  corresponding Calculator methods.
end note

note right of "scientific"
  src/operations/scientific.py
  Standalone implementations of power, logarithm
  (base-10), and natural_logarithm — mirror of
  the corresponding Calculator methods.
end note

"arithmetic" ..> CalculationEngine : delegates to module-level _engine

class "__main__" as Main {
    +main(argv: list[str] | None) : void
}

note right of Main::main
  Instantiates OperationHistory, ErrorLogger,
  Calculator, and CalculatorContext, then
  clears history/error state.
  REPL mode: argv is empty or ["--repl"].
  CLI mode: argv has operation + operands.
  Exit codes: 0=ok, 1=usage, 2=unknown op,
  3=invalid operands, 4=operation error.
end note

